d":288939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2194072c2119868127b541fda0597c03ca71775","tid":1486003,"uid":55425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:26:55.000Z","msg":"有冇小朋友？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:30:43.000Z","msg":"有，但已分居咗n年，而呢n年耐大家無見過面同聯絡過"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:25:20.000Z","msg":"搵何君堯啦，拋妻棄子搵返d人渣做岩架喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:28:17.000Z","msg":"唔係我拋，當年雙方都有問題經常家暴，我就帶走個女"},{"pid":"9c7e8e0f5572b5425b727e8e7a06968059300725","tid":1486003,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:28:42.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSst8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=f1d0d461\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSst8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=f1d0d461\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"102ee8ad982093bf34981cd05361ca34b1f54b3d","tid":1486003,"uid":288939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5b713087109887f30e316daa5e7dc66c7f53cc1","tid":1486003,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"782031a476531cb9eac122543df8ec262162ea12","tid":1486003,"uid":288939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2194072c2119868127b541fda0597c03ca71775","tid":1486003,"uid":55425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:26:55.000Z","msg":"有冇小朋友？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:30:43.000Z","msg":"有，但已分居咗n年，而呢n年耐大家無見過面同聯絡過"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:25:20.000Z","msg":"搵何君堯啦，拋妻棄子搵返d人渣做岩架喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:30:41.000Z","msg":"重點係唔想再冋所謂前夫聯絡，局住搵律師搞"}]}